02:49.830 --> 02:51.411
You need to kill yourself.

02:51.580 --> 02:54.743
It's really the only solution
for any of us.

02:54.920 --> 02:59.675
I mean, look, I have tried four times,
and they keep saving me.

02:59.840 --> 03:01.580
Do it now,
while you have a chance.

03:05.310 --> 03:07.050
Just give me the go-ahead,
and it's done.

03:07.220 --> 03:08.881
Was that a nod?

03:09.060 --> 03:09.970
No.

03:10.230 --> 03:11.094
Yes?

03:12.900 --> 03:13.855
Hey! Hey!

03:14.770 --> 03:16.681
Simon, no!

03:17.940 --> 03:19.521
