09:02.790 --> 09:03.950
Okay.

09:04.410 --> 09:05.661
But I was so cold.

09:06.920 --> 09:09.286
I was thirsty, hungry.

09:09.460 --> 09:11.291
I... I had to try.

09:12.460 --> 09:13.540
