09:13.880 --> 09:15.086
To survive.

09:16.970 --> 09:18.426
I stepped out, but the...

09:19.810 --> 09:21.801
The snow was so deep,
the wind, I...

09:22.890 --> 09:24.175
I kept on falling, and...

09:26.310 --> 09:27.846
